If possible, FastAPI should avoid relying on Pydantic's internals ([e.g. `eval_type_lenient`](https://github.com/fastapi/fastapi/blob/d7f88623e1304667c67da17dfd278b5099522ef9/fastapi/_compat.py#L57), which we had to deprecate instead of removing it even if it was an internal function). Our type evaluation logic is subject to changes as we'll have to adapt to PEP 649.

